<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>HopeReach ‚Äì Empowering Campaigns, Rebuilding Lives</title>
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
    }

    body {
      background-color: #f9fafb;
      color: #333;
    }

    header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 20px 60px;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 100;
    }

    .logo {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #007b7f;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 25px;
    }

    .nav-links a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #007b7f;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .cta {
      background-color: #00a5a7;
      color: white;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 25px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
      transition: 0.3s;
    }

    .cta:hover {
      background-color: #007b7f;
    }

    .hero {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 80px 60px;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(0,123,127,0.8), rgba(255,255,255,0.1)), url('hero.jpg') center/cover no-repeat;
      color: white;
    }

    .hero-content {
      max-width: 550px;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 3rem;
      line-height: 1.2;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .hero p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .hero a {
      background-color: #ffffff;
      color: #007b7f;
      padding: 12px 25px;
      border-radius: 30px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
      transition: 0.3s;
    }

    .hero a:hover {
      background-color: #007b7f;
      color: white;
    }

    .testimonials {
      background-color: #f0fdfd;
      padding: 60px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .testimonials h2 {
      color: #007b7f;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .footer {
      background-color: #003c3d;
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 25px;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .hero {
        flex-direction: column;
        padding: 60px 30px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .hero-content {
        max-width: 100%;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <div class="logo">üåø HopeReach</div>
    <nav class="nav-links">
      <a href="#">Coopattisk</a>
      <a href="#">Hopewunding</a>
      <a href="#">Freand Jours</a>
      <a href="#">About</a>
    </nav>
    <a href="#" class="cta">Shop Now</a>
  </header>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1>Empowering Campaigns.<br>Rebuilding Lives.</h1>
      <p>HopeReach connects campaigns, communities, and change-makers. Together, we bring hope and rebuild lives with purpose.</p>
      <a href="#">Get Started</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="testimonials">
    <h2>What People Are Saying</h2>
    <p>‚ÄúHopeReach helped us raise funds and rebuild faster than we ever imagined.‚Äù</p>
    <p>‚ÄúA community that truly cares and connects people to change.‚Äù</p>
  </section>

  <footer class="footer">
    ¬© 2025 HopeReach. All Rights Reserved.
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
